(110, 9, 'abstract', 'In less than 100 years, BC wine has risen from nowhere to prominence. With over 200 wineries today, BC is fast becoming a premier wine region in the new world. Furthermore, the provincial government’s recent regulatory reform sets the stage for a major shift in the industry, fueling growth. Now, we aim to change the way you buy wine with New District. '),
