(38, 1, '2014-03-24 10:43:22', '2014-03-24 10:43:22', 'Welcome to New District.\n\nWe travel British Columbia to find the best wines our province has to offer. We visit wineries, meet creative people behind them, try their wines and bring it all to you. Best of all, we give you access to great wines, from carefully selected wineries, and deliver them directly to your door.\n\nSign up to follow our travels and stay updated on our wine selection.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 10:43:22', '2014-03-24 10:43:22', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=38', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(39, 1, '2014-03-22 11:51:33', '2014-03-22 11:51:33', 'New District is an online farmers’ market of boutique BC wineries, which will provide an unparalleled experience for discovering locally produced wine. On New District, you will buy directly from the producer, allowing you to enjoy unique products often not available on store shelves. We have built the most convenient way to buy BC-produced wine online, with the products arriving right to your door. While we build out this platform, we invite you to explore and purchase from just some of BC’s great boutique wineries.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-22 11:51:33', '2014-03-22 11:51:33', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=39', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
