(65, 1, '2014-03-24 03:39:39', '2014-03-24 03:39:39', 'Welcome to New District. We are an online farmers’ market of boutique BC wineries, providing an unparalleled experience for discovering locally produced wine. On New District, you will buy directly from the producer, allowing you to enjoy unique products often not available on store shelves. We have built the most convenient way to buy BC-produced wine online, with the products arriving right to your door. While we build out this platform, we invite you to explore and purchase from just some of BC’s great boutique wineries.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 03:39:39', '2014-03-24 03:39:39', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=65', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
