(88, 1, '2014-03-24 09:11:21', '2014-03-24 09:11:21', 'Welcome to New District.\r\n\r\nWe travel British Columbia to bring you the best wines our province has to offer. We visit the wineries, meet the craftspeople, learn their history and bring it all to you. Best of all, we give you access to the best wines from carefully selected wineries and deliver them directly to your door.\r\n\r\nSign up to follow our travels and stay updated on our wine selection.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 09:11:21', '2014-03-24 09:11:21', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=88', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
