(103, 1, '2014-03-24 10:03:59', '2014-03-24 10:03:59', 'Welcome to New District.\r\n\r\nWe travel British Columbia to find the best wines our province has to offer. We visit wineries, meet craftspeople, learn history and bring it all to you. Best of all, we give you access to great wines, from carefully selected wineries and deliver them directly to your door.\r\n\r\nSign up to follow our travels and stay updated on our wine selection.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 10:03:59', '2014-03-24 10:03:59', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=103', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
