(150, 1, '2014-03-25 00:37:07', '2014-03-25 00:37:07', 'Our search for great BC wineries has so far resulted in enlisting the wineries below on New District. We are constantly in the process of adding more winemakers who share the passion for local, high-quality wine. Within each winery shop, you will find great wines that you will have a very hard time spotting at your local liquor store.', 'Our Wineries', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-wineries', '', '', '2014-03-25 12:13:42', '2014-03-25 12:13:42', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=150', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(151, 1, '2014-03-25 00:37:07', '2014-03-25 00:37:07', 'The following are the wineries we have partnered with to bring you their products. Follow through to see them in more detail, look at through their vineyards and history and see their products. Naturally you can purchase any of the wines and we will deliver them right to your door.\r\n\r\nCheck back with us, as we will be adding more in the the coming weeks.', 'Our Wineries', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '150-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-25 00:37:07', '2014-03-25 00:37:07', '', 150, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=151', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(152, 1, '2014-03-25 01:58:21', '2014-03-25 01:58:21', 'Welcome to New District.\r\n\r\nWe travel British Columbia to find the best wines our province has to offer. We visit vineyards, meet creative people behind them, learn their stories, and bring it all to you. Best of all, we give you access to great wines, from carefully selected wineries, and deliver them directly to your door.\r\n\r\nSign up to follow our travels and stay updated on our wine selection.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-25 01:58:21', '2014-03-25 01:58:21', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=152', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(153, 1, '2014-03-25 01:58:58', '2014-03-25 01:58:58', 'Welcome to New District.\r\n\r\nWe travel British Columbia to find the best wines our province has to offer. We visit vineyards, meet the talented people behind them, learn their stories, and bring it all to you. Best of all, we give you access to great wines, from carefully selected wineries, and deliver them directly to your door.\r\n\r\nSign up to follow our travels and stay updated on our wine selection.', 'From The Editor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-25 01:58:58', '2014-03-25 01:58:58', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.65/journal-newdistrict/?p=153', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
